1
00:02:07,880 --> 00:02:08,759
Meng Jingu,

2
00:02:09,039 --> 00:02:09,699
and Gong Yu,

3
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,210
are our new classmates.

4
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,000
Get along well with each other from now on.

5
00:02:13,000 --> 00:02:15,460
Let's welcome them with a round of applause.

6
00:02:17,480 --> 00:02:19,640
This is so unreal.

7
00:02:19,720 --> 00:02:21,440
He actually transferred to our class.

8
00:02:21,440 --> 00:02:22,240
Oh my God.

9
00:02:22,600 --> 00:02:24,760
Could it be because I didn't return his umbrella?

10
00:02:24,760 --> 00:02:25,920
Please introduce yourselves.

11
00:02:25,920 --> 00:02:28,040
Hello everyone, my name is Meng Jingu.

12
00:02:28,040 --> 00:02:29,800
I just transferred from Peiying Middle School.

13
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,660
Please take care of me from now on.

14
00:02:31,760 --> 00:02:33,040
Hello everyone, I'm Gong Yu,

15
00:02:33,040 --> 00:02:34,079
a sports student.

16
00:02:34,160 --> 00:02:35,690
My grades are just average.

17
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:36,800
For basketball

18
00:02:37,000 --> 00:02:38,520
or fights, you can call me.

19
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:39,400
Gong Yu,

20
00:02:40,200 --> 00:02:41,520
what are you talking about?

21
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:42,880
You come to school to study hard,

22
00:02:42,880 --> 00:02:43,720
not to fight.

23
00:02:43,960 --> 00:02:45,820
If you fight, see how I punish you.

24
00:02:51,040 --> 00:02:52,240
No fighting.

25
00:02:56,240 --> 00:02:57,120
Meng Jingu,

26
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,579
go to the second row

27
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,640
and share a desk with Xiong Yuanbao.

28
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,680
Okay, sir.

29
00:03:08,640 --> 00:03:10,560
Gong Yu, go to the last row

30
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:12,530
and share a desk with Wang Zhiyong.

31
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:13,960
Don't cause trouble.

32
00:03:22,560 --> 00:03:24,520
Why don't you leave the umbrella with me,

33
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:25,920
so it doesn't bother you?

34
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,800
Wait.

35
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:37,600
What's wrong?

36
00:03:37,600 --> 00:03:38,960
Watch out for the car.

37
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:55,200
Class,

38
00:03:56,880 --> 00:03:58,540
open yesterday's exam paper.

39
00:04:01,960 --> 00:04:02,840
Meng Jingu,

40
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,800
share with Xiong Yuanbao for now.

41
00:04:04,800 --> 00:04:05,800
After class,

42
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:08,160
go to the office to get a new copy.

43
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,900
What are you two doing?

44
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:18,959
Gong Yu, share with Wang Zhiyong for now.

45
00:04:21,920 --> 00:04:24,180
Many of you got the first question wrong.

46
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,720
Why would you choose B?

47
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:36,120
Mr. Tian,

48
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:38,400
I want to go back to my original seat.

49
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:40,880
Mu Qingjun.

50
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,200
You are quite a smart kid.

51
00:04:43,320 --> 00:04:44,560
Why can't you put that intelligence

52
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,620
into your studies?

53
00:04:45,640 --> 00:04:46,680
Sleeping in class

54
00:04:46,880 --> 00:04:48,240
doesn't just affect you,

55
00:04:48,240 --> 00:04:50,120
it affects the teachers and other students.

56
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,680
You're like a rat in a soup pot.

57
00:04:51,680 --> 00:04:53,540
Is it okay to ruin the whole class?

58
00:04:54,840 --> 00:04:57,040
If you say I'm a rat in a soup pot,

59
00:04:57,440 --> 00:05:00,840
what does that make the other teachers and students?

60
00:05:01,080 --> 00:05:02,340
They are, of course...

61
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:05,940
You... are you talking back to me?

62
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:06,800
Mr. Tian,

63
00:05:07,520 --> 00:05:08,520
I promise

64
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:10,560
I'll never sleep in class again.

65
00:05:10,800 --> 00:05:11,720
I promise.

66
00:05:12,640 --> 00:05:13,970
You've made a truckload

67
00:05:14,080 --> 00:05:15,240
of promises to me.

68
00:05:15,440 --> 00:05:17,100
How many of them were sincere?

69
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:18,440
Previously,

70
00:05:18,440 --> 00:05:19,560
when you sat with Xiong Yuanbao,

71
00:05:19,560 --> 00:05:21,680
you endlessly asked her for tutoring.

72
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:22,610
Didn't you know?

73
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:24,480
Her grades aren't much better than yours.

74
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,120
Aren't you just holding her back?

75
00:05:26,120 --> 00:05:26,920
Tell you what.

76
00:05:27,280 --> 00:05:27,960
Don't you want to go back?

77
00:05:27,960 --> 00:05:28,600
Sure.

78
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:30,360
In this monthly exam,

79
00:05:30,360 --> 00:05:31,880
if you improve your rank by 10 places,

80
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:33,040
I'll let you move back.

81
00:05:33,040 --> 00:05:34,080
If not,

82
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:36,440
you'll stay in the isolation zone and reflect on yourself.

83
00:05:36,440 --> 00:05:37,920
T-Ten places?

84
00:05:38,400 --> 00:05:39,080
What?

85
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,060
Is that too few?

86
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,560
N-No.

87
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:45,000
L-Let me think about it.

88
00:05:45,640 --> 00:05:46,480
Wait, Mu Qingjun.

89
00:05:46,480 --> 00:05:48,320
Am I begging you?

90
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,440
Alright.

91
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:52,159
Ten places it is.

92
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:53,360
Brat.

93
00:05:53,640 --> 00:05:54,560
Anything else?

94
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:56,280
Go back.

95
00:06:09,560 --> 00:06:10,400
Mr. Tian.

96
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,360
I came to pick up the test papers.

97
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,800
Meng Jingu,

98
00:06:14,320 --> 00:06:15,580
with such good grades,

99
00:06:15,880 --> 00:06:17,410
you must set a good example.

100
00:06:17,880 --> 00:06:19,520
Okay, Mr. Tian.

101
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,900
Is that the Gong Yu you mentioned?

102
00:06:26,480 --> 00:06:27,840
Keep your voice down.

103
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,480
Look how happy you are.

104
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,600
Well,

105
00:06:33,400 --> 00:06:34,530
what a coincidence.

106
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,280
About last time,

107
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:38,409
I haven't had a chance to thank you.

108
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,960
No need, it was nothing.

109
00:06:40,240 --> 00:06:41,280
You are...

110
00:06:41,720 --> 00:06:43,520
I'm Tong Ruirui.

111
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:46,240
Tong as in Tong Ruirui, Rui as in Tong Ruirui.

112
00:06:53,840 --> 00:06:56,760
Tong as in Tong Ruirui, Rui as in Tong Ruirui.

113
00:06:57,280 --> 00:06:58,960
It sounds like a poem.

114
00:07:00,280 --> 00:07:02,200
Is that what I just said?

115
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:04,760
You know, life

116
00:07:04,760 --> 00:07:06,890
is really more dramatic than a TV show.

117
00:07:07,080 --> 00:07:08,760
Do you know that Meng Jingu?

118
00:07:09,000 --> 00:07:10,840
The one who saved me in Shanghai.

119
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,370
The umbrella is his.

120
00:07:12,680 --> 00:07:14,080
Really?

121
00:07:14,680 --> 00:07:16,400
A city-level merit student,

122
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:17,760
he saved you,

123
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:19,280
and now he's your deskmate.

124
00:07:19,280 --> 00:07:21,400
Even novels wouldn't dare to write it like this.

125
00:07:21,400 --> 00:07:23,680
Right? I think it's amazing too.

126
00:07:24,960 --> 00:07:25,840
Do you think

127
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,360
we both got

128
00:07:27,400 --> 00:07:29,840
shot by Cupid?

129
00:07:30,120 --> 00:07:32,400
With a shotgun, no less.

130
00:07:32,560 --> 00:07:33,360
That's just you.

131
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,890
I don't have such thoughts.

132
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,050
If it's me, then it's me.

133
00:07:37,159 --> 00:07:38,760
If it's me, then it's me.

134
00:07:40,440 --> 00:07:42,520
The exams have different difficulty levels.

135
00:07:42,520 --> 00:07:44,280
Advancing by exactly ten places

136
00:07:44,280 --> 00:07:46,120
is really hard to control.

137
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:47,920
What else can I do?

138
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,920
I can't just watch Yuanbao

139
00:07:50,120 --> 00:07:51,920
meet the wrong guy and go astray.

140
00:07:52,880 --> 00:07:54,760
Before, to make Yuanbao tutor you,

141
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:57,620
you'd always score just a few points lower than her.

142
00:07:57,800 --> 00:07:58,960
But this time is different.

143
00:07:58,960 --> 00:08:01,680
You are controlling your score against the whole class.

144
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:02,610
It's almost like

145
00:08:03,960 --> 00:08:05,440
putting a satellite into orbit.

146
00:08:05,440 --> 00:08:07,040
As a physics genius,

147
00:08:07,080 --> 00:08:08,410
if you improve too much,

148
00:08:08,840 --> 00:08:09,800
you'll be exposed.

149
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:11,360
If you improve too little, less than ten places,

150
00:08:11,360 --> 00:08:13,280
won't all your efforts be in vain?

151
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:15,360
This is too hard.

152
00:08:16,760 --> 00:08:18,760
I'm trying to figure something out.

153
00:08:20,320 --> 00:08:21,920
What if you let everyone know

154
00:08:21,920 --> 00:08:22,720
that actually

155
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,620
your physics grades are really good?

156
00:08:25,640 --> 00:08:26,700
What would happen?

157
00:08:27,440 --> 00:08:29,400
I think Yuanbao would hate me to death.

158
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:31,530
What about the college entrance exam?

159
00:08:33,919 --> 00:08:35,250
We still have two years.

160
00:08:35,600 --> 00:08:36,760
There will be a way.

161
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,320
You

162
00:08:38,640 --> 00:08:40,000
must keep it a secret for me,

163
00:08:40,000 --> 00:08:42,080
no matter how well you knew Meng Jingu before.

164
00:08:42,080 --> 00:08:42,760
Got it?

165
00:08:43,480 --> 00:08:44,480
Don't worry, bro.

166
00:08:54,200 --> 00:08:54,840
What is it?

167
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,920
This is what Ruirui waited a long time for

168
00:09:01,920 --> 00:09:03,520
and said she'd show me later.

169
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,600
But what are these?

170
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:16,560
Are you sure these are the most popular

171
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,160
novels that girls like to read nowadays?

172
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,000
Don't worry.

173
00:09:19,160 --> 00:09:20,720
I asked over 10 girls.

174
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:22,240
I am 100 percent sure.

175
00:09:24,320 --> 00:09:25,120
Buying books?

176
00:09:25,360 --> 00:09:26,000
Yes.

177
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,640
I want the latest girls' magazines you have here,

178
00:09:28,640 --> 00:09:30,760
like Hua Huo, Meng Ya,

179
00:09:30,880 --> 00:09:31,800
and Zhi Yin.

180
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:34,770
Okay, the magazines you want are all here.

181
00:09:34,840 --> 00:09:35,960
Anything else?

182
00:09:38,880 --> 00:09:40,160
My Sunshine,

183
00:09:40,560 --> 00:09:41,560
My Sun...

184
00:09:45,600 --> 00:09:48,680
The Boss's Little Wife.

185
00:09:50,400 --> 00:09:52,640
Little... Wife.

186
00:09:55,080 --> 00:09:58,140
It's all written here anyway. Please help me find them.

187
00:09:59,240 --> 00:10:00,920
The handwriting is so crooked.

188
00:10:00,920 --> 00:10:03,600
You better read it to me and I'll find them for you.

189
00:10:03,600 --> 00:10:05,460
Forget it, I'll find them myself.

190
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:08,520
My School Hunk,

191
00:10:08,680 --> 00:10:10,680
Gentle Love from the Prince?

192
00:10:10,800 --> 00:10:13,400
Young man, are you the one reading these?

193
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,920
Just ring me up quickly.

194
00:10:15,920 --> 00:10:17,120
Stop nagging.

195
00:10:18,840 --> 00:10:21,440
Slow Love from Bossy Husband.

196
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:24,320
For you and your bestie,

197
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:26,520
I cashed in a lot of favors.

198
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:27,440
Thanks.

199
00:10:28,840 --> 00:10:31,240
Alright, let me ask you something serious.

200
00:10:31,280 --> 00:10:31,880
Go ahead.

201
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:35,560
What do you think of Gong Yu?

202
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:39,880
Handsome, sports student.

203
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:41,640
Tell me something I don't know.

204
00:10:41,640 --> 00:10:43,170
Transferred from Peiying.

205
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:45,180
Are you doing this on purpose?

206
00:10:46,480 --> 00:10:48,140
The former top guy at Peiying.

207
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,370
What did you say?

208
00:10:49,480 --> 00:10:50,740
Taekwondo black belt.

209
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:53,440
His combat skills are about the same as mine,

210
00:10:53,440 --> 00:10:55,100
but his grades are just as bad.

211
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:57,720
As for him,

212
00:10:58,240 --> 00:10:59,720
he's tough and doesn't talk much.

213
00:10:59,720 --> 00:11:00,920
Not easy to approach,

214
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:02,560
but he should be quite loyal.

215
00:11:03,040 --> 00:11:05,770
Otherwise, how could he be the top guy at Peiying?

216
00:11:06,040 --> 00:11:06,680
By the way,

217
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,200
tell Tong Ruirui

218
00:11:08,680 --> 00:11:10,080
to stay away from Gong Yu.

219
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,120
A guy like Gong Yu

220
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:14,040
is not someone an innocent girl like her should mess with.

221
00:11:14,040 --> 00:11:15,280
What are you talking about?

222
00:11:15,280 --> 00:11:16,810
Ruirui didn't ask me to ask.

223
00:11:16,840 --> 00:11:17,640
Come on.

224
00:11:17,800 --> 00:11:18,930
Look at Tong Ruirui,

225
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:20,880
she can't take her eyes off him.

226
00:11:23,360 --> 00:11:24,360
You noticed?

227
00:11:24,760 --> 00:11:25,760
What do you think?

228
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:31,800
Ghost!

229
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:33,280
Mu Qingjun!

230
00:11:33,280 --> 00:11:33,960
Come catch me!

231
00:11:33,960 --> 00:11:35,890
If you catch me, I'll buy you a cake.

232
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,920
Stop right there.

233
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,640
Still running!

234
00:11:41,600 --> 00:11:43,760
I have a cousin who goes to Peiying.

235
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,880
He knows Gong Yu.

236
00:11:45,360 --> 00:11:48,120
I heard that when he was at Peiying,

237
00:11:48,240 --> 00:11:49,640
he had a bad reputation.

238
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,320
A bad reputation?

239
00:11:51,840 --> 00:11:53,040
I heard he stole money

240
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:54,280
and even hit girls.

241
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,720
Really? No way.

242
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:58,480
That's the rumor.

243
00:11:58,560 --> 00:12:00,000
Who knows if it's true?

244
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:03,000
It seems you can't judge a book by its cover.

245
00:12:03,160 --> 00:12:04,200
How could this be?

246
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,800
Hitting girls?

247
00:12:13,360 --> 00:12:14,680
Stay away from Gong Yu.

248
00:12:15,000 --> 00:12:15,720
Someone like Gong Yu

249
00:12:15,720 --> 00:12:17,960
is not someone a delicate girl like her can mess with.

250
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,320
No, no.

251
00:12:23,880 --> 00:12:25,200
Yuanbao, go back to your seat.

252
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,530
Class is about to start.

253
00:12:30,920 --> 00:12:32,560
Class, next week

254
00:12:32,680 --> 00:12:34,640
is our first monthly exam of this semester.

255
00:12:34,640 --> 00:12:36,480
You all know where you ranked

256
00:12:36,560 --> 00:12:38,160
in our class last semester, right?

257
00:12:38,160 --> 00:12:39,560
I hope this semester,

258
00:12:39,800 --> 00:12:41,280
you can work hard and endure hardships.

259
00:12:41,280 --> 00:12:42,200
As the saying goes,

260
00:12:42,200 --> 00:12:43,760
many hands make light work.

261
00:12:43,880 --> 00:12:44,800
If each of you

262
00:12:44,920 --> 00:12:46,120
takes a small step forward,

263
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:47,480
it will be a giant leap

264
00:12:47,640 --> 00:12:48,920
for our class.

265
00:12:49,240 --> 00:12:50,000
I hope

266
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,040
our class this semester

267
00:12:51,040 --> 00:12:52,360
can make it into the top six.

268
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,160
I still

269
00:12:53,440 --> 00:12:54,770
have confidence in you.

270
00:12:56,840 --> 00:12:57,570
Who laughed?

271
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:00,440
Ignorant.

272
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:02,490
Holding us back.

273
00:13:02,760 --> 00:13:03,640
Who laughed?

274
00:13:04,600 --> 00:13:05,600
Have you no shame?

275
00:13:06,240 --> 00:13:08,760
You are literally the worst class I've ever taught.

276
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:10,680
Especially with you black sheep.

277
00:13:11,200 --> 00:13:12,480
The bottom few in this monthly exam

278
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,320
must bring your parents.

279
00:13:13,320 --> 00:13:15,050
I will talk to them personally.

280
00:13:16,080 --> 00:13:17,410
To improve your grades,

281
00:13:17,600 --> 00:13:19,360
the other teachers and I have decided

282
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:21,120
to form mutual study groups.

283
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:23,680
I'll read the list now.

284
00:13:24,160 --> 00:13:24,960
For Group 1,

285
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:26,160
the leaders

286
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:28,160
are Xing Yaqi and Meng Jingu.

287
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:30,480
The members are Xiong Yuanbao,

288
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:31,640
Tong Ruirui,

289
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,840
Shang Ningyu,

290
00:13:33,440 --> 00:13:34,300
and Mu Qingyun.

291
00:13:34,360 --> 00:13:35,200
Zhang Dongbo.

292
00:13:36,520 --> 00:13:38,680
Group Two. Leader, Qiao Yan.

293
00:13:39,400 --> 00:13:40,960
Member, Gong Yu.

294
00:13:41,080 --> 00:13:43,480
Group Four. Leader, Zhou Mengzhi.

295
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,880
Members,

296
00:13:45,440 --> 00:13:46,240
Wang Zhiyong,

297
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,520
Zhang Ming.

298
00:13:50,280 --> 00:13:51,080
Ruirui.

299
00:13:51,800 --> 00:13:53,440
Ruirui, where have you been?

300
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:54,600
I've been looking for you.

301
00:13:54,600 --> 00:13:55,960
I have something to tell you.

302
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:58,840
Yuanbao, I have something to tell you too.

303
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:00,720
What is it?

304
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:05,720
I just applied to Mr. Tian.

305
00:14:06,400 --> 00:14:09,040
I'm going to study in Group Two.

306
00:14:11,000 --> 00:14:12,400
For Gong Yu?

307
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,520
No, Ruirui.

308
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:17,880
I don't want you to get hurt.

309
00:14:18,200 --> 00:14:19,560
Get hurt?

310
00:14:20,440 --> 00:14:21,720
What do you mean?

311
00:14:22,360 --> 00:14:24,880
Actually, Gong Yu is not who you think he is.

312
00:14:25,200 --> 00:14:27,130
Don't be fooled by his appearance.

313
00:14:28,640 --> 00:14:30,600
Did Qingjun tell you something?

314
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:31,960
No.

315
00:14:33,000 --> 00:14:34,800
I was in the restroom

316
00:14:35,160 --> 00:14:37,290
and heard two girls talking about him.

317
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:39,880
What did they say?

318
00:14:40,840 --> 00:14:41,720
They said

319
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,560
when Gong Yu was at Peiying,

320
00:14:45,800 --> 00:14:47,720
he not only stole money

321
00:14:48,560 --> 00:14:49,760
but also hit girls.

322
00:14:50,480 --> 00:14:51,740
Xiong Yuanbao, right?

323
00:14:57,880 --> 00:14:59,600
Do you know how terrible it is to talk behind someone's back

324
00:14:59,600 --> 00:15:01,520
and spread rumors?

325
00:15:02,960 --> 00:15:04,000
You think just because you're a girl,

326
00:15:04,000 --> 00:15:05,320
I won't touch you?

327
00:15:05,480 --> 00:15:06,740
I dare you to touch her.

328
00:15:11,480 --> 00:15:12,940
It's a misunderstanding.

329
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,160
Go.

330
00:15:16,680 --> 00:15:17,360
Go.

331
00:15:17,760 --> 00:15:18,920
Sorry.

332
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:19,880
Sorry.

333
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:20,600
Gong Yu.

334
00:15:23,200 --> 00:15:24,560
I think you're great.

335
00:15:24,920 --> 00:15:26,960
You're not like what they say.

336
00:15:29,880 --> 00:15:30,920
Ruirui, let's go.

337
00:15:36,040 --> 00:15:37,360
I will hit girls.

338
00:15:38,080 --> 00:15:39,810
Your name is Mu Qingjun, right?

339
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:41,530
Keep an eye on her yourself.

340
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:51,120
Ruirui, I'm sorry.

341
00:15:51,520 --> 00:15:52,800
I only heard about it.

342
00:15:52,840 --> 00:15:54,600
It's for your own good, Ruirui.

343
00:15:57,680 --> 00:15:58,400
Ruirui.

344
00:16:00,120 --> 00:16:01,880
Listen to me, Ruirui.

345
00:16:15,040 --> 00:16:15,760
Ruirui.

346
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:18,000
What I told you today,

347
00:16:18,160 --> 00:16:20,080
I wasn't trying to badmouth him.

348
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,040
I'm genuinely worried about you.

349
00:16:22,040 --> 00:16:23,160
Don't get me wrong.

350
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:38,720
Yuanbao.

351
00:16:39,400 --> 00:16:41,280
I know you're looking out for me,

352
00:16:41,760 --> 00:16:44,320
but I still can't believe

353
00:16:44,480 --> 00:16:46,520
that someone who'd protect a strange girl

354
00:16:46,520 --> 00:16:47,920
would do such things.

355
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,120
I think

356
00:16:49,520 --> 00:16:51,400
I should get to know him better.

357
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:54,120
He's probably not what he seems to be.

358
00:16:54,840 --> 00:16:55,900
As for this matter,

359
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,960
please don't interfere anymore.

360
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,640
Thank you.

361
00:17:00,400 --> 00:17:02,760
Oh no. She's obsessed.

362
00:17:03,360 --> 00:17:06,040
She's putting me on the opposing side.

363
00:17:26,160 --> 00:17:28,600
Sorry, I zoned out again.

364
00:17:28,960 --> 00:17:32,000
Yuanbao, why is Ruirui in Group Two?

365
00:17:34,280 --> 00:17:35,080
What's wrong?

366
00:17:35,440 --> 00:17:36,440
Are you okay?

367
00:17:37,320 --> 00:17:38,160
I'm fine.

368
00:17:39,640 --> 00:17:41,440
In ancient times, scholars always had teachers.

369
00:17:41,440 --> 00:17:44,000
A teacher is one who propagates doctrines, imparts professional knowledge, and resolves doubts.

370
00:17:44,000 --> 00:17:45,320
Since people are not born with knowledge,

371
00:17:45,320 --> 00:17:46,400
who can be without doubts?

372
00:17:46,400 --> 00:17:48,360
If one has doubts but does not learn from a teacher, their doubts

373
00:17:48,360 --> 00:17:49,360
will never be resolved.

374
00:17:49,360 --> 00:17:50,560
For those born before me,

375
00:17:50,560 --> 00:17:52,720
they naturally learned the truth before me,

376
00:17:52,720 --> 00:17:54,450
so I follow them as my teachers.

377
00:17:54,840 --> 00:17:55,760
Well...

378
00:17:55,960 --> 00:17:58,480
For those born after me,

379
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:00,520
and I follow,

380
00:18:00,840 --> 00:18:02,440
I follow them as my teachers.

381
00:18:04,960 --> 00:18:06,000
I learn the truth,

382
00:18:06,440 --> 00:18:09,600
so why should I care if they were born before or after me?

383
00:18:12,200 --> 00:18:13,000
Where are we?

384
00:18:18,200 --> 00:18:19,160
I don't know.

385
00:18:19,480 --> 00:18:23,720
Ten, nine, eight, seven, six...

386
00:18:23,880 --> 00:18:27,680
Five, four, three, two, one.

387
00:18:27,800 --> 00:18:33,600
Sing, sing, sing.

388
00:18:33,760 --> 00:18:35,720
Mu Qingyun, can I join your group?

389
00:18:38,760 --> 00:18:39,600
Sure.

390
00:18:39,800 --> 00:18:42,200
What do you want to sing? I'll sing with you.

391
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,850
Let's sing that one.

392
00:18:45,560 --> 00:18:48,840
Every time,

393
00:18:48,960 --> 00:18:52,000
I stay strong through wandering and loneliness.

394
00:18:52,160 --> 00:18:58,080
Every time, even when hurt, I don't shed a tear.

395
00:18:58,280 --> 00:19:04,640
I know I've always had a pair of invisible wings.

396
00:19:04,840 --> 00:19:06,560
Fly with me,

397
00:19:06,720 --> 00:19:09,880
past the despair.

398
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,760
Not bad. You have talent.

399
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:15,760
Didn't they almost get into a fight a few days ago?

400
00:19:15,840 --> 00:19:18,120
Why are they suddenly singing together now?

401
00:19:18,120 --> 00:19:19,000
At this moment,

402
00:19:19,120 --> 00:19:21,160
I just want to ask the scriptwriter of my life,

403
00:19:21,160 --> 00:19:22,160
could the things happening to me

404
00:19:22,160 --> 00:19:23,620
be any more melodramatic?

405
00:19:23,760 --> 00:19:24,820
Let's go, Qingjun.

406
00:19:28,480 --> 00:19:29,560
Let's go, Qingjun.

407
00:19:30,400 --> 00:19:31,260
School is over.

408
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:33,000
Ruirui, bye-bye.

409
00:19:33,680 --> 00:19:34,160
Bye-bye.

410
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:35,160
Yuanbao, I'm leaving.

411
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:35,920
Bye-bye.

412
00:19:42,560 --> 00:19:43,490
Ruirui, Ruirui.

413
00:19:43,560 --> 00:19:44,280
Ruirui.

414
00:19:45,640 --> 00:19:47,600
Can you just listen to my advice?

415
00:19:47,840 --> 00:19:48,680
Yuanbao.

416
00:19:49,520 --> 00:19:51,650
You don't have to persuade me anymore.

417
00:19:51,680 --> 00:19:53,160
I know what I want to do.

418
00:20:04,600 --> 00:20:05,320
Oh no.

419
00:20:05,480 --> 00:20:06,540
Ruirui is missing.

420
00:20:25,520 --> 00:20:26,160
Gong Yu.

421
00:20:28,120 --> 00:20:28,840
Um...

422
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,200
You saved me last time.

423
00:20:31,520 --> 00:20:33,780
I haven't had the chance to thank you yet.

424
00:20:34,520 --> 00:20:35,320
So,

425
00:20:36,600 --> 00:20:37,520
this is for you.

426
00:20:51,320 --> 00:20:53,000
You've been here for so many days,

427
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:54,930
and don't really have any friends.

428
00:20:55,040 --> 00:20:56,240
So I was wondering...

429
00:20:57,320 --> 00:20:59,080
Can I be your friend?

430
00:20:59,640 --> 00:21:01,170
I understand what you mean.

431
00:21:01,680 --> 00:21:02,800
But,

432
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:05,600
I don't really like making friends with girls.

433
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,120
I appreciate the thought.

434
00:21:09,080 --> 00:21:10,360
As for this scarf,

435
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,900
I don't like black either.

436
00:21:11,960 --> 00:21:13,890
You should give it to someone else.

437
00:21:35,600 --> 00:21:36,400
Ruirui.

438
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,760
Ruirui.

439
00:21:38,160 --> 00:21:39,020
I'm right here.

440
00:21:39,160 --> 00:21:41,200
Wait for me there. Don't leave.

441
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:55,320
Why are you here?

442
00:21:55,520 --> 00:21:57,120
You're asking me why I'm here?

443
00:21:57,120 --> 00:21:58,320
Why are you here?

444
00:21:58,760 --> 00:22:00,960
I finally found you. I was worried sick.

445
00:22:03,360 --> 00:22:04,420
Why are you crying?

446
00:22:05,080 --> 00:22:06,740
What's wrong? What happened?

447
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:08,060
Did someone bully you?

448
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:11,440
I'm fine.

449
00:22:12,080 --> 00:22:14,800
Didn't you say you'd take me to check out cram schools?

450
00:22:14,800 --> 00:22:16,880
I waited for you for a long time, but you didn't show up.

451
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:18,720
I called you, but you didn't answer.

452
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:20,000
So I called Yuanbao.

453
00:22:20,280 --> 00:22:21,960
Yuanbao called your home.

454
00:22:22,080 --> 00:22:24,210
And we found out you weren't even home.

455
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:26,080
Everyone was so worried.

456
00:22:26,160 --> 00:22:27,160
We all came out looking for you.

457
00:22:27,160 --> 00:22:29,080
We were afraid something had happened.

458
00:22:29,080 --> 00:22:30,480
Yuanbao came out too?

459
00:22:31,200 --> 00:22:32,440
My phone died.

460
00:22:32,520 --> 00:22:34,850
I didn't know you guys were looking for me.

461
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:36,520
I made you worry.

462
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,640
I'm sorry.

463
00:22:38,280 --> 00:22:38,960
Alright.

464
00:22:39,640 --> 00:22:42,170
As long as you're okay, nothing else matters.

465
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:43,680
Let's go. I'll take you home.

466
00:22:43,680 --> 00:22:45,560
You should tell Yuanbao first.

467
00:22:45,680 --> 00:22:46,920
Don't let her worry.

468
00:22:47,040 --> 00:22:47,880
Right.

469
00:22:48,600 --> 00:22:50,660
Yuanbao was just crying out of worry.

470
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:53,040
She cried out of worry?

471
00:22:53,320 --> 00:22:54,240
Of course.

472
00:22:54,280 --> 00:22:56,210
Aren't you two as close as sisters?

473
00:22:59,920 --> 00:23:00,520
Yuanbao.

474
00:23:00,720 --> 00:23:02,080
I found it.

475
00:23:17,040 --> 00:23:18,080
Here you go.

476
00:23:26,720 --> 00:23:29,160
Sisters are the best.

477
00:23:30,440 --> 00:23:31,760
What's wrong, Ruirui?

478
00:23:32,200 --> 00:23:33,200
What happened?

479
00:23:33,960 --> 00:23:35,680
Last night,

480
00:23:36,160 --> 00:23:38,960
I went to tell Gong Yu

481
00:23:39,200 --> 00:23:41,560
that I wanted to be friends,

482
00:23:42,520 --> 00:23:44,080
but I was rejected.

483
00:23:44,680 --> 00:23:45,960
I told you

484
00:23:46,040 --> 00:23:47,840
he doesn't have good character.

485
00:23:47,880 --> 00:23:48,680
Why did you...

486
00:23:49,480 --> 00:23:50,440
All right.

487
00:23:50,800 --> 00:23:52,800
Even if his character isn't bad,

488
00:23:53,240 --> 00:23:54,600
and we misunderstood him,

489
00:23:54,600 --> 00:23:55,320
but

490
00:23:55,520 --> 00:23:56,760
why would he refuse

491
00:23:56,840 --> 00:23:58,100
to be friends with you?

492
00:23:58,560 --> 00:23:59,690
What was his reason?

493
00:24:00,800 --> 00:24:01,480
He said

494
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:04,290
he doesn't like being friends with girls.

495
00:24:04,640 --> 00:24:06,040
You're missing the point.

496
00:24:06,040 --> 00:24:07,240
What do you mean?

497
00:24:07,960 --> 00:24:10,360
I feel like Gong Yu joined our group

498
00:24:10,560 --> 00:24:11,680
not because of you,

499
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:13,410
but for something else.

500
00:24:14,680 --> 00:24:15,640
Something else?

501
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:18,800
He came for Mu Qingjun.

502
00:24:21,000 --> 00:24:21,800
Right.

503
00:24:22,360 --> 00:24:24,760
They were at each other's throats the other day

504
00:24:24,760 --> 00:24:26,620
and almost fought because of you.

505
00:24:27,000 --> 00:24:28,130
What a coincidence.

506
00:24:28,480 --> 00:24:29,880
Let me ask you something.

507
00:24:29,960 --> 00:24:31,160
Did you see Mutou?

508
00:24:31,360 --> 00:24:32,840
I just saw Qingyun

509
00:24:32,880 --> 00:24:34,320
and Gong Yu

510
00:24:34,400 --> 00:24:35,400
going to the roof.

511
00:24:35,800 --> 00:24:37,240
The roof?

512
00:24:37,560 --> 00:24:38,090
Let's go.

513
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:38,960
Let's go.

514
00:24:39,240 --> 00:24:39,800
Hurry up.

515
00:24:39,880 --> 00:24:40,480
Follow me.

516
00:24:45,920 --> 00:24:47,280
Since you are in Zhicheng,

517
00:24:47,280 --> 00:24:48,940
I will protect you from now on.

518
00:24:49,560 --> 00:24:50,880
Okay, I'll rely on you.

519
00:24:59,000 --> 00:24:59,800
Yuanbao,

520
00:25:00,440 --> 00:25:01,760
how did they

521
00:25:02,640 --> 00:25:04,760
become so close?

522
00:25:17,680 --> 00:25:18,880
What are you reading?

523
00:25:19,080 --> 00:25:20,920
Studying so hard?

524
00:25:26,680 --> 00:25:27,640
What are you writing?

525
00:25:27,640 --> 00:25:29,300
Questions from someone else.

526
00:25:29,640 --> 00:25:30,600
Oh my god.

527
00:25:30,880 --> 00:25:33,010
They are actually studying together.

528
00:25:35,040 --> 00:25:37,320
Not even this serious with me.

529
00:25:41,040 --> 00:25:41,760
No.

530
00:25:42,240 --> 00:25:43,360
I have to find a way.

531
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,920
I can't tell Ruirui.

532
00:25:58,120 --> 00:25:58,920
Gamma.

533
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:01,960
Him again. Interesting.

534
00:26:03,480 --> 00:26:04,800
For the sharks,

535
00:26:04,800 --> 00:26:06,800
what a feast of a day this is.

536
00:26:06,840 --> 00:26:08,840
There's more food than they can eat.

537
00:26:08,840 --> 00:26:09,700
Don't eat this.

538
00:26:10,200 --> 00:26:11,360
You go get a new one.

539
00:26:16,320 --> 00:26:18,680
Grandma, didn't I tell you?

540
00:26:18,720 --> 00:26:21,180
Eating expired food will give you diarrhea.

541
00:26:22,080 --> 00:26:23,480
Today is the last day.

542
00:26:23,520 --> 00:26:25,000
Only after tonight

543
00:26:25,080 --> 00:26:26,160
will it be expired.

544
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:28,000
We can't waste food.

545
00:26:28,360 --> 00:26:29,960
I'll eat it. You get a new one.

546
00:26:34,200 --> 00:26:35,330
Then I'll eat it too.

547
00:26:36,080 --> 00:26:37,810
It's faster if we eat together.

548
00:26:39,880 --> 00:26:41,240
The monthly exams are coming up soon, right?

549
00:26:41,240 --> 00:26:42,680
The shark doesn't care.

550
00:26:42,960 --> 00:26:43,960
There's still a lot of food.

551
00:26:43,960 --> 00:26:45,240
You need to be sensible

552
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:46,680
and study hard.

553
00:26:46,960 --> 00:26:47,960
Ask your teachers

554
00:26:48,200 --> 00:26:51,000
and good classmates for more advice.

555
00:26:53,080 --> 00:26:53,960
Besides,

556
00:26:54,240 --> 00:26:56,440
Qingyun's family has helped us so much.

557
00:26:56,760 --> 00:26:58,800
You should help him out too.

558
00:26:59,880 --> 00:27:01,200
Don't worry, Grandma.

559
00:27:02,520 --> 00:27:04,850
I will definitely supervise and push him.

560
00:27:06,880 --> 00:27:07,920
Good kid.

561
00:27:27,320 --> 00:27:29,960
If there are three long options and one short option, choose the shortest one.

562
00:27:29,960 --> 00:27:33,840
If there are three short options and one long option, choose the longest one.

563
00:27:33,840 --> 00:27:36,040
The answer to this question should be C.

564
00:27:42,720 --> 00:27:44,780
This question is quite interesting.

565
00:27:54,280 --> 00:27:55,920
Brother, please help me.

566
00:28:04,440 --> 00:28:05,040
Come.

567
00:28:05,560 --> 00:28:07,620
Let's see how you guys did on the exam.

568
00:28:15,600 --> 00:28:17,480
I will work harder next time.

569
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:19,280
I won't get so many questions wrong again.

570
00:28:19,280 --> 00:28:20,240
Xiong Yuanbao.

571
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:23,380
You're tenth from the bottom and still talking?

572
00:28:23,400 --> 00:28:24,400
Go stand at the back.

573
00:28:24,400 --> 00:28:25,040
Me?

574
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,840
What are you laughing at?

575
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:29,320
The bottom ten students in this monthly exam,

576
00:28:29,320 --> 00:28:31,120
go stand at the back and reflect.

577
00:28:31,840 --> 00:28:33,570
You guys are really something.

578
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:36,000
Class One surpassed us again.

579
00:28:36,000 --> 00:28:37,600
You've completely embarrassed me.

580
00:28:37,600 --> 00:28:39,560
The bottom ten must bring their parents.

581
00:28:39,560 --> 00:28:41,490
We're in this together, brothers.

582
00:28:41,720 --> 00:28:42,720
Shang Ningyu,

583
00:28:42,920 --> 00:28:45,680
you're at the bottom and still have the nerve to talk?

584
00:28:45,680 --> 00:28:46,800
Whenever you guys get together,

585
00:28:46,800 --> 00:28:48,080
you just can't keep your mouths shut.

586
00:28:48,080 --> 00:28:50,410
Truly a few bad apples spoiling the bunch.

587
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:54,440
Mu Qingyun totally crushed it.

588
00:28:54,440 --> 00:28:56,100
I'm sure everyone has seen it.

589
00:28:56,520 --> 00:28:58,920
This time, I must praise Mu Qingyun.

590
00:29:00,600 --> 00:29:01,320
Where is he?

591
00:29:02,080 --> 00:29:03,280
Sir, he

592
00:29:03,360 --> 00:29:04,520
said he

593
00:29:05,240 --> 00:29:06,370
went to get some sun.

594
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:08,200
What's everyone laughing at?

595
00:29:08,200 --> 00:29:10,400
Although Mu Qingyun usually goofs off,

596
00:29:10,480 --> 00:29:11,610
he moved up 13 places

597
00:29:11,720 --> 00:29:12,920
in this monthly exam,

598
00:29:13,120 --> 00:29:15,280
and he even solved the last major physics question.

599
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,040
Look at yourselves,

600
00:29:16,040 --> 00:29:17,200
especially you guys.

601
00:29:17,200 --> 00:29:19,000
Mr. Tian, you must be mistaken.

602
00:29:19,200 --> 00:29:20,440
Yeah, Mr. Tian.

603
00:29:20,520 --> 00:29:22,560
That's an out-of-syllabus physics question.

604
00:29:22,560 --> 00:29:24,320
Could Mu Qingyun have cheated?

605
00:29:24,920 --> 00:29:26,280
Don't slander people.

606
00:29:26,440 --> 00:29:28,160
How is that slander?

607
00:29:28,440 --> 00:29:29,640
During the exam,

608
00:29:29,760 --> 00:29:32,240
Mu Qingyun sat right in front of Meng Jingu.

609
00:29:32,440 --> 00:29:34,720
And they were the only two who got it right.

610
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:36,000
That's very strange.

611
00:29:38,120 --> 00:29:39,320
The answering steps.

612
00:29:40,120 --> 00:29:41,850
They are indeed quite similar.

613
00:29:43,280 --> 00:29:44,040
Impossible.

614
00:29:44,640 --> 00:29:46,200
Mu Qingyun would not cheat.

615
00:29:48,920 --> 00:29:50,450
If he really wanted to cheat

616
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:52,560
and cared that much about his grades,

617
00:29:52,560 --> 00:29:54,890
he wouldn't rank at the bottom every time.

618
00:29:55,280 --> 00:29:58,120
You only see the side of him that skips classes, fights,

619
00:29:58,120 --> 00:29:59,280
and plays games.

620
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,200
But who knows that

621
00:30:01,280 --> 00:30:02,560
before the exam,

622
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:05,450
he studied in the library late into the night?

623
00:30:06,200 --> 00:30:08,400
Maybe he has done this question before.

624
00:30:08,640 --> 00:30:09,560
Or maybe

625
00:30:10,280 --> 00:30:11,520
he is just smart.

626
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:13,600
But he could never have cheated.

627
00:30:13,600 --> 00:30:15,080
I swear on my honor,

628
00:30:15,120 --> 00:30:16,720
he is not that kind of person.

629
00:30:17,160 --> 00:30:18,160
You have no proof.

630
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,880
How can you slander him like this?

631
00:30:19,880 --> 00:30:22,040
Exactly. Mu Qingyun didn't cheat.

632
00:30:22,120 --> 00:30:23,180
I trust my brother.

633
00:30:23,440 --> 00:30:24,160
I trust him too.

634
00:30:24,160 --> 00:30:24,690
Exactly.

635
00:30:24,720 --> 00:30:26,120
What's the use of your trust?

636
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:27,640
Show us the proof.

637
00:30:27,840 --> 00:30:29,880
Who has proof that he didn't cheat?

638
00:30:29,920 --> 00:30:30,800
If you say so,

639
00:30:30,840 --> 00:30:32,720
show us the proof that he cheated.

640
00:30:33,160 --> 00:30:35,480
His usual test scores are the proof.

641
00:30:35,560 --> 00:30:36,920
We all know that.

642
00:30:37,400 --> 00:30:39,160
Mutou wouldn't cheat.

643
00:30:39,600 --> 00:30:41,060
He wouldn't stoop to that.

644
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:42,640
I know his character.

645
00:30:42,800 --> 00:30:44,240
To slander him without proof,

646
00:30:44,240 --> 00:30:45,600
isn't it a bit too much?

647
00:30:46,280 --> 00:30:47,680
It's my first time seeing

648
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:48,760
someone

649
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:50,440
so brave,

650
00:30:51,000 --> 00:30:53,880
taking another person's side without asking questions.

651
00:30:53,880 --> 00:30:55,360
This reckless courage

652
00:30:55,480 --> 00:30:56,760
and unwavering faith

653
00:30:57,200 --> 00:30:59,720
make her shine brightly

654
00:30:59,960 --> 00:31:01,720
and look especially cute right now.

655
00:31:01,720 --> 00:31:03,120
All right, stop arguing.

656
00:31:04,360 --> 00:31:05,280
Meng Jingu.

657
00:31:06,080 --> 00:31:07,010
During the exam,

658
00:31:07,400 --> 00:31:09,000
Mu Qingjun was sitting right in front of you.

659
00:31:09,000 --> 00:31:10,160
Whether he cheated or not,

660
00:31:10,160 --> 00:31:11,360
you must know best.

661
00:31:20,760 --> 00:31:22,160
Mr. Tian, Mu Qingjun...

662
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:23,000
Reporting.

663
00:31:25,160 --> 00:31:26,420
You finally showed up.

664
00:31:26,760 --> 00:31:28,560
I should get a note from the principal

665
00:31:28,560 --> 00:31:29,560
and have you expelled.

666
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:32,320
Sir, I promise I won't be late next time.

667
00:31:34,760 --> 00:31:36,880
Perfect timing. We were just discussing your exam.

668
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:39,120
Sir, I heard everything at the door.

669
00:31:42,320 --> 00:31:44,560
Thank you all for your trust,

670
00:31:45,000 --> 00:31:46,600
but I have to disappoint you.

671
00:31:47,680 --> 00:31:49,080
I did copy Meng's paper.

672
00:31:58,320 --> 00:31:59,880
It really is his handwriting.
